<taxonomicName id="94C24D25FFFCFFE2E1FD00CDFDBBFF73" authority="Herz, 1899" authorityName="Herz" authorityYear="1899" box="[199,536,150,177]" class="Insecta" family="Nymphalidae" genus="Melitaea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="29" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="phoebe" subSpecies="tungusa">
<emphasis id="61B6EAB4FFFCFFE2E1FD00CDFE3FFF72" bold="true" box="[199,412,150,177]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="29">M.phoebe tungusa</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="37534B57FFFCFFE2E09A00CDFDBBFF73" author="Herz, O." box="[416,536,150,177]" pageId="4" pageNumber="29" pagination="209 - 265" refId="ref9249" refString="Herz, O. (1899) Reise nach Nordost-Sibirien in das Lenagebiet in den Jahren 1888 und 1889 nebst einem Verzeichnisse der dort erbeuteten Macrolepidopteren. Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift Iris, 11, 209 - 265." type="journal article" year="1899">Herz,1899</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="1BD8652DFFFCFFE2E32100CDFCA5FDDA" pageId="4" pageNumber="29" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="537D36A6FFFCFFE2E32100CDFCA5FDDA" blockId="4.[151,1437,150,537]" pageId="4" pageNumber="29">
[TL: 
<collectingCountry id="2BD57636FFFCFFE2E36800CCFC8BFF73" box="[594,808,150,176]" name="Russia" pageId="4" pageNumber="29">Russian Federation</collectingCountry>
,Yakutia,River Witim];wing morphology and particularly the club shaped antenna indicate that this subspecies is referable to 
<taxonomicName id="94C24D25FFFCFFE2E2AF00E1FBAFFF17" baseAuthorityName="Denis &amp; Schiffermuller" baseAuthorityYear="1775" box="[917,1036,186,212]" class="Insecta" family="Nymphalidae" genus="Melitaea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="29" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="phoebe">
<emphasis id="61B6EAB4FFFCFFE2E2AF00E1FBAFFF17" box="[917,1036,186,212]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="29">M. phoebe</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Lukhtanov here designates a male as 
<typeStatus id="8C798804FFFCFFE2E18C0084FEBEFF3B" box="[182,285,222,248]" pageId="4" pageNumber="29">lectotype</typeStatus>
for the name 
<emphasis id="61B6EAB4FFFCFFE2E0820085FDB2FF3B" box="[440,529,223,248]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="29">tungusa</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="37534B57FFFCFFE2E3220085FD34FF3B" author="Herz, O." box="[536,663,222,249]" pageId="4" pageNumber="29" pagination="209 - 265" refId="ref9249" refString="Herz, O. (1899) Reise nach Nordost-Sibirien in das Lenagebiet in den Jahren 1888 und 1889 nebst einem Verzeichnisse der dort erbeuteten Macrolepidopteren. Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift Iris, 11, 209 - 265." type="journal article" year="1899">Herz, 1899</bibRefCitation>
. The 
<typeStatus id="8C798804FFFCFFE2E3EE0084FC98FF3B" box="[724,827,222,248]" pageId="4" pageNumber="29">lectotype</typeStatus>
is shown in 
<figureCitation id="CBF92A23FFFCFFE2E2F30084FB29FF3A" box="[969,1162,222,249]" captionStart="FIGURES 7–11" captionStartId="4.[151,264,1857,1881]" captionTargetBox="[152,1436,560,1833]" captionTargetId="figure-219@4.[151,1436,560,1833]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 7–11. 7, Lectotype of Melitaea phoebe sibina Alphéraky, 1881. 8, Melitaea phoebe ab. tatara Krulikovsky, 1891. 9, Lectotype of Melitaea phoebe ornata Christoph, 1893. 10, Lectotype of Melitaea phoebe uralensis Krulikovsky, 1897 (= ufensis Krulikovsky 1902). 11, Lectotype of Melitaea phoebe var. tungusa Herz, 1899. Figs 7, 9, 11 © V.A. Lukhtanov. Figs 8, 10 © expired. A = upperside, B = underside, C = labels on specimen pin." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6577635" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6577635/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="29">Figures 11A &amp; B</figureCitation>
, together with the labels (
<figureCitation id="CBF92A23FFFCFFE2E19A0158FEA7FEDF" box="[160,260,258,284]" captionStart="FIGURES 7–11" captionStartId="4.[151,264,1857,1881]" captionTargetBox="[152,1436,560,1833]" captionTargetId="figure-219@4.[151,1436,560,1833]" captionTargetPageId="4" captionText="FIGURES 7–11. 7, Lectotype of Melitaea phoebe sibina Alphéraky, 1881. 8, Melitaea phoebe ab. tatara Krulikovsky, 1891. 9, Lectotype of Melitaea phoebe ornata Christoph, 1893. 10, Lectotype of Melitaea phoebe uralensis Krulikovsky, 1897 (= ufensis Krulikovsky 1902). 11, Lectotype of Melitaea phoebe var. tungusa Herz, 1899. Figs 7, 9, 11 © V.A. Lukhtanov. Figs 8, 10 © expired. A = upperside, B = underside, C = labels on specimen pin." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6577635" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6577635/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="29">Fig. 11C</figureCitation>
). The labels on the pin are as follows: (1) on red paper handwritten in black “ 
<typeStatus id="8C798804FFFCFFE2E55A0158FB71FEDF" box="[1120,1234,258,284]" pageId="4" pageNumber="29">Lectotype</typeStatus>
/ 
<taxonomicName id="94C24D25FFFCFFE2E5DB0158FF42FE83" authority="Knock" authorityName="Knock" class="Insecta" family="Nymphalidae" genus="Melitaea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="29" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="phoebe">Melitaea Phoebe Knock</taxonomicName>
/ 
<taxonomicName id="94C24D25FFFCFFE2E1C8017DFE62FE83" authority="Herz" authorityName="Herz" authorityYear="1899" box="[242,449,294,321]" class="Insecta" family="Nymphalidae" genus="Melitaea" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="29" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="variety" species="phoebe" variety="tungusa">var. Tungusa Herz</taxonomicName>
/ V. Lukhtanov design; (2) on black-edged white paper, printed in black “Кол.[лекциЯ] Вел.[икого] Кн.[ЯЗЯ]/ НиколаЯ/ Михайловича” (translates to: Collection of Grand Duke Nikolai Mikhailovich); (3) on white paper with a broad black surround printed in black on the upperside “Witim” and on the underside “O. Herz”; (4) on white paper (discolouring to brown) handwritten in black “1/12/7” (This means: 01 July [1888] (old style)/12 July [1888] (new style). No year is given on the data label but it can be deduced from 
<bibRefCitation id="37534B57FFFCFFE2E5E901EDFA3BFE13" author="Herz, O." box="[1235,1432,438,465]" pageId="4" pageNumber="29" pagination="209 - 265" refId="ref9249" refString="Herz, O. (1899) Reise nach Nordost-Sibirien in das Lenagebiet in den Jahren 1888 und 1889 nebst einem Verzeichnisse der dort erbeuteten Macrolepidopteren. Deutsche Entomologische Zeitschrift Iris, 11, 209 - 265." type="journal article" year="1899">Herz (1899: 240)</bibRefCitation>
. This diagnosis agrees with those of 
<bibRefCitation id="37534B57FFFCFFE2E3180180FCA5FE37" author="Higgins, L. G." box="[546,774,474,500]" pageId="4" pageNumber="29" pagination="175 - 365" refId="ref9372" refString="Higgins, L. G. (1941) An illustrated catalogue of the Palearctic Melitaea (Lep. Rhopalocera). Transactions of the Royal Entomological Society of London, 91, 175 - 365. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1365 - 2311.1941. tb 01045. x" type="journal article" year="1941">Higgins (1941: 342)</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="37534B57FFFCFFE2E22B0180FBFEFE37" author="Korb, S. K. &amp; Bolshakov, L. V." box="[785,1117,474,500]" pageId="4" pageNumber="29" pagination="1 - 123" refId="ref9703" refString="Korb, S. K. &amp; Bolshakov, L. V. (2011) A catalogue of butterflies (Lepidoptera: Papilioformes) of the former USSR. Second edition, reformatted and updated. Eversmannia Supplement 2, 1 - 123. [In Russian]" type="journal article" year="2011">Korb &amp; Bolshakov (2011: 41)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="37534B57FFFCFFE2E5AB0181FEB3FDDA" author="Van Oorschot, H. &amp; Coutsis, J. G." pageId="4" pageNumber="29" refId="ref11693" refString="Van Oorschot, H. &amp; Coutsis, J. G. (2014) The genus Melitaea Fabricius, 1807 (Lepidoptera, Nymphalidae, Nymphalinae) Taxonomy and systematics with special reference to the male genitalia. Tshikolovets publications, Pardubice, Czech Republic, 360 pp." type="book" year="2014">van Oorschot &amp; Coutsis (2014: 60)</bibRefCitation>
; not considered by 
<bibRefCitation id="37534B57FFFCFFE2E0D301A4FCA1FDDA" author="Hesselbarth, G. &amp; van Oorschot, H. &amp; Wagener, S." box="[489,770,510,537]" pageId="4" pageNumber="29" pagination="1 - 847" refId="ref9287" refString="Hesselbarth, G., van Oorschot, H. &amp; Wagener, S. (1995) Die Tagfalter der Turkei unter Berucksichtigung der angrenzenden Lander, Sigbert Wagener, Bocholt, Germany, 1, 1 - 757, 2, 758 - 1354, 3, 1 - 847." type="journal article" year="1995">
Hesselbarth 
<emphasis id="61B6EAB4FFFCFFE2E34F01A5FD05FDDB" box="[629,678,510,536]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="29">et al</emphasis>
. (1995)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
